State Regulations

Before amending or repealing an
administrative rule of an Appellate Division for the efficient and orderly
transaction of business in the trial courts, including but not limited to
calendar practice, that was in effect on March 31, 1978, the Chief Judge or

Chief Administrator shall consult with that Appellate
